festival.introText:
Glastonbudget, the Mecca of Tribute, has been running for over a decade and will see approximately 15,000 fans flock to see more than 130 amazing bands play 5 stages. 

The ‘Daddy of Tribute’ has always been about great music, great value, and we are very excited to watch it grow year on year. Last year was yet another triumphant success, which leads us nicely into this, the eleventh anniversary. Expect big things, at minimal prices.
festival.descriptionText: Skiddle is an official ticket outlet of Glastonbudget 2016. Get Glastonbudget tickets, news and information with Skiddle.com

faqs.question: When is Glastonbudget 2023?
faqs.answer: Glastonbudget takes place on Friday 26th May - Sunday 28th May 2023.

faqs.question: Where is Glastonbudget?
faqs.answer: Glastonbudget is located at Turnpost Farm in Wymeswold, Leicestershire, England.
